Tasman Series|Tasman Series]]\n|align=\"center\" style=\"background:#ffdf9f;\"| 3rd\n|rowspan=2| [[Mildren Mono]] [[Waggott Engineering|Waggott TC4V]]\n|rowspan=2| [[Alec Mildren Racing]]\n|-\n| [[1970 Australian Drivers' Championship|Australian Drivers' Championship]]\n|align=\"center\" | 9th\n|-\n!rowspan=2| 1971\n| [[1971 Tasman Series|Tasman Series]]\n|align=\"center\" | 5th\n| [[Mildren (racing cars)|Mildren]] (Franklen) [[Chevrolet Small-Block engine|Chevrolet]]\n| [[Alec Mildren Racing]]\n|-\n| [[1971 Australian Drivers' Championship|Australian Drivers' Championship]]\n|align=\"center\" style=\"background:#dfdfdf;\"| '''2nd'''\n| [[McLaren]] M10B [[Chevrolet Small-Block engine|Chevrolet]]\n| Kevin Bartlett Shell Racing\n|-\n!rowspan=3| 1972\n| [[1972 Tasman Series|Tasman Series]]\n|align=\"center\" | 5th\n| [[McLaren]] M10B [[Chevrolet Small-Block engine|Chevrolet]]\n| Kevin Bartlett Shell Racing\n|-\n| [[1972 Australian Drivers' Championship|Australian Drivers' Championship]]\n|align=\"center\" style=\"background:#dfdfdf;\"| '''2nd'''\n| [[Lola Cars|Lola]] T300 [[Chevrolet Small-Block engine|Chevrolet]]\n| Shell / Chesterfield Racing\n|-\n| [[1972 L&M Continental 5000 Championship|L&M Continental 5000 Championship]]\n|align=\"center\" | 18th <ref>Wolfgang Klopfer, Formula A and Formula 5000 in America: Race by Race, page 60</ref>\n| [[McLaren]] M10B [[Chevrolet Small-Block engine|Chevrolet]] &<br />[[Lola Cars|Lola]] T300 [[Chevrolet Small-Block engine|Chevrolet]]\n| Eisert Jones Racing<br />Kevin Bartlett\n|-\n!rowspan=2| 1973\n| [[1973 Tasman Series|Tasman Series]]\n|align=\"center\" | 11th\n|rowspan=2| [[Lola Cars|Lola]] T300 [[Chevrolet Small-Block engine|Chevrolet]]\n|rowspan=2| Chesterfield Filter Racing\n|-\n| [[1973 Australian Drivers' Championship|Australian Drivers' Championship]]\n|align=\"center\" | 7th\n|-\n! 1974\n| [[1974 Australian Drivers' Championship|Australian Drivers' Championship]]\n|align=\"center\" style=\"background:#dfdfdf;\"| '''2n