\u00fcrburgring Touring Car Grand Prix|NUR]]\n| [[1987 Spa 24 Hour|SPA]]\n| [[1987 Grand Prix Brno|BNO]]\n| [[1987 WTCC Silverstone|SIL]]\n|style=\"background:#efcfff;\"| [[1987 James Hardie 1000|BAT]]<br>{{small|Ret}}\n|style=\"background:#efcfff;\"| [[1987 Bob Jane T-Marts 500|CLD]]<br>{{small|Ret}}\n| [[1987 Wellington 500|WEL]]\n| [[1987 Fuji InterTEC 500|FJI]]\n! NC\n! 0\n|}\n\n===Complete Asia-Pacific Touring Car Championship results===\n([[:Template:Motorsport driver results legend|key]]) (Races in '''bold''' indicate pole position) (Races in ''italics'' indicate fastest lap)\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"text-align:center; font-size:95%\"\n! Year\n! Team\n! Car\n! 1\n! 2\n! 3\n! 4\n! DC\n! Points\n|-\n! [[Asia-Pacific Touring Car Championship|1988]]\n! {{flagicon|AUS}} [[Bob Forbes Racing]]\n! [[Holden VL Commodore SS Group A SV]]\n|style=\"background:#cfcfff;\"| [[1988 Bathurst 1000|BAT]]<br>{{small|14}}\n| [[Wellington 500|WEL]]\n| [[Pukekohe Park Raceway|PUK]]\n| [[Fuji Speedway|FJI]]\n! NC\n! 0\n|}\n\n===Complete Bathurst 500/1000 results===\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"font-size:90%\"\n|-\n! Year\n! Car#\n! Team\n! Co-Drivers\n! Car\n! Class\n! Laps\n! {{Tooltip|Pos.|Overall Position}}\n! {{Tooltip|Class<br>Pos.|Class Position}}\n|- align=\"center\"\n! [[1963 Armstrong 500|1963]]\n| 16\n|align=\"left\"|\n|align=\"left\"| {{Flagicon|AUS}} [[Bill Reynolds (racing driver)|Bill Reynolds]]\n|align=\"left\"| [[Holden EH 179]]\n| C\n| 115\n| ''NA''\n| 7th\n|- align=\"center\"\n! [[1965 Armstrong 500|1965]]\n| 55\n|align=\"left\"| {{flagicon|AUS}} [[British Motor Corporation (Australia)|BMC]]\n|align=\"left\"| {{Flagicon|AUS}} [[Ron Haylen]]\n|align=\"left\"| [[Mini|Morris Mini de Luxe]]\n| A\n| 111\n| 28th\n| 6th\n|- align=\"center\"\n! [[1966 Gallaher 500|1966]]\n| 8\n|align=\"left\"| \n|align=\"left\"| {{Flagicon|AUS}} [[John Harvey (racing driver)|John Harvey]]\n|align=\"left\"| [[Volvo Amazon|Volvo 122S]]\n| D\n| 119\n| 15th\n| 4th\n|- align=\"center\